snippet.textDisplay: I am a proud Pakistani but i would like to say some home truths here. So far season 10 has been disappointing. What's the point in having background singers if you can't hear them? They were more prominent in season 9. I agree with others that this song lacked energy and did not do the original justice. Also I have noticed in this season a lot of 'artists' are relatives of well established artists and I wonder whether the likes of Danyal Zafar, Ali Sethi, Zaw Ali etc would ever have qualified for Coke Studio had they not had a famous relative in the music business. This makes me sick because there is real talent out there in Pakistan but these so called 'artists' who have not shown their worth prior to this get to steal their spot in the limelight
